&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consultant Community Pediatrician/ Specialty Doctor with special interest in Neurodevelopmental disorders (10PA)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will aim to support the development of integrated care pathways for children with Neurodevelopmental needs with CAMHS, local services and education. It would be desirable to have additional training in the use of specific diagnostic tools , competencies and clinical experience in assessment of children with social and communication difficulties. The applicant will be clinically active in children’s neurodevelopment and disability services. The applicant will be clinically competent in meeting the health needs have looked after children and will also contribute towards health assessments and provision of reports for EHC needs assessments. The timetable is flexible, and can be modified to reflect the special interests and expertise of the appointee.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameSandhya JoseJob titleConsultant PaediatricianEmail addresssandhya.jose@hey.nhs.ukTelephone number01482 602673&lt;/p&gt;
